page.title: 19THE CHURCH FETE
page.content: Stephanie & I went down to{Monk {Fryston Square}at 2.30pm. Stephanie & I entered the fancy dress competition. Stephanie was dressed up as the devil. I was dressed up as a jack in a box. There were{three floats.}One for the band. One for the{Queen (Lisa Murray) and her attendants. The last one was for the fancy dress. The floats went down to{Hillam Square}& then turned round & went back to the old vicarage. Monk Fryston{ballet school}danced a little play for us. The summer picture competition & fancy dress were judged. Stephanie & I went to get changed. I had 2 lollies to eat. I bought some bubble bath & I had a go on the teddy bears picnic game.
